Class Order

  • java.lang.Object
    • entities.Order

  • public class Order
extends java.lang.Object
    this class represents order object- it has variables that we need to save an order. we use this classe's instance in order to build the orders table- in "follow orders". every variable has its getters and setters, we call this class's constructor in "ClientFollowOrdersC".
